  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The ratio of <span class=\"italic\">t</span> to <span class=\"italic\">u</span> is 1 to 2, and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"t equals 10\"></span></span>. What is the value of <span class=\"italic\">u</span> ?</p>\n",
